---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="テニス練習メモ" description="テニスの練習メモブログ" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <style is:global>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      body {
        background: #0a0a0a !important;
        color: #f0f0f0 !important;
        font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif !important;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        width: 100% !important;
        max-width: 100% !important;
      }

      /* Astroデフォルトのmain幅制限を解除 */
      body > main,
      main {
        width: 100% !important;
        max-width: 100% !important;
        margin: 0 !important;
        padding: 0 !important;
      }

      /* ===== HERO ===== */
      .t-hero {
        position: relative;
        width: 100vw;
        margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
        min-height: 92vh;
        display: flex !important;
        align-items: center !important;
        justify-content: center !important;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 5rem 1rem 4rem;
      }

      /* グリッド背景 */
      .t-grid {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
          linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 60px 60px;
        z-index: 0;
      }

      /* ネットライン */
      .t-netline {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0; left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 90%;
        height: 2px;
        background: #c8ff50;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(200,255,80,0.6);
        z-index: 1;
      }

      /* 回転サークル */
      .t-ring {
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 50%;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
      }
      .t-ring-1 {
        width: 500px; height: 500px;
        top: -150px; right: -100px;
        border: 1.5px solid rgba(200,255,80,0.15);
        animation: tRing 25s linear infinite;
      }
      .t-ring-2 {
        width: 300px; height: 300px;
        bottom: 20px; left: -80px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        animation: tRing 18s linear infinite reverse;
      }
      @keyframes tRing {
        from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
        to   { transform: rotate(360deg); }
      }

      /* テニスボール */
      .t-ball {
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 32%, #e2ff5a, #9dc918);
        z-index: 2;
        pointer-events: none;
      }
      .t-ball::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 18%; left: 6%;
        width: 88%; height: 55%;
        border-top: 2.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
        border-radius: 50%;
        transform: rotate(-28deg);
      }
      .t-ball-1 {
        width: 58px; height: 58px;
        top: 15%; left: 6%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(200,255,80,0.55);
        animation: tFloat1 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      }
      .t-ball-2 {
        width: 34px; height: 34px;
        bottom: 18%; right: 8%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(200,255,80,0.4);
        animation: tFloat2 5.5s ease-in-out 0.8s infinite;
      }
      .t-ball-3 {
        width: 20px; height: 20px;
        top: 60%; right: 18%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(200,255,80,0.3);
        animation: tFloat1 7s ease-in-out 2s infinite;
      }

      @keyframes tFloat1 {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
        50%       { transform: translateY(-24px) rotate(200deg); }
      }
      @keyframes tFloat2 {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
        50%       { transform: translateY(-16px) rotate(-160deg); }
      }

      /* ===== ヒーローテキスト（完全中央） ===== */
      .t-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .t-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.35em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #c8ff50;
        border: 1px solid rgba(200,255,80,0.45);
        padding: 5px 18px;
        border-radius: 99px;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: tUp 0.6s ease 0.1s forwards;
      }

      .t-title {
        font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7.5rem);
        line-height: 1.0;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: tUp 0.7s ease 0.2s forwards;
      }
      .t-title .t-accent {
        color: #c8ff50;
        display: block;
        text-shadow:
          0 0 40px rgba(200,255,80,0.6),
          0 0 80px rgba(200,255,80,0.25);
      }

      .t-desc {
        margin-top: 1.75rem;
        font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 2vw, 1rem);
        color: rgba(240,240,240,0.5);
        line-height: 1.9;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        text-align: center;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: tUp 0.7s ease 0.35s forwards;
      }

      .t-btn {
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        background: #c8ff50;
        color: #0a0a0a;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 15px 40px;
        border-radius: 3px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: tUp 0.7s ease 0.5s forwards;
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      }
      .t-btn::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.28);
        transform: translateX(-110%) skewX(-15deg);
        transition: transform 0.4s;
      }
      .t-btn:hover::before { transform: translateX(110%) skewX(-15deg); }
      .t-btn:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(200,255,80,0.45);
      }

      @keyframes tUp {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
        to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
      }

      /* ===== STATS ===== */
      .t-stats {
        background: #0f0f0f;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,255,80,0.18);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,255,80,0.18);
        padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 8rem);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        width: 100vw;
        margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
      }
      .t-stat { text-align: center; }
      .t-stat-n {
        font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        color: #c8ff50;
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      }
      .t-stat-l {
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.22em;
        color: rgba(240,240,240,0.38);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-top: 5px;
      }

      /* ===== CARDS ===== */
      .t-features {
        padding: 5rem 2rem;
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .t-sec-badge {
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.3em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #c8ff50;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
      .t-sec-title {
        font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem);
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        color: #f0f0f0;
      }
      .t-cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        gap: 1px;
        background: rgba(200,255,80,0.1);
      }
      .t-card {
        background: #0d0d0d;
        padding: 2.25rem 1.75rem;
        text-align: left;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: background 0.25s;
      }
      .t-card:hover { background: #131313; }
      .t-card::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0; left: 0;
        height: 2px; width: 0;
        background: #c8ff50;
        transition: width 0.4s;
      }
      .t-card:hover::after { width: 100%; }
      .t-card-ico { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .t-card-ttl {
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        color: #f0f0f0;
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      }
      .t-card-txt {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: rgba(240,240,240,0.45);
        line-height: 1.85;
      }

      /* ===== CTA ===== */
      .t-cta-wrap {
        padding: 0 2rem 5rem;
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .t-cta {
        background: linear-gradient(130deg, #c8ff50 0%, #8dcc00 100%);
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 3.5rem 3rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 2rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .t-cta::after {
        content: 'TENNIS';
        position: absolute;
        right: -10px; bottom: -28px;
        font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
        font-size: 8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
        line-height: 1;
        pointer-events: none;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }
      .t-cta-h {
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
        color: #0a0a0a;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }
      .t-cta-p { color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); margin-top: 0.4rem; font-size: 0.88rem; }
      .t-cta-btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: #0a0a0a;
        color: #c8ff50;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.13em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 30px;
        border-radius: 3px;
        white-space: nowrap;
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      }
      .t-cta-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
    </style>

    <Header />
    <main>

      <!-- HERO -->
      <section class="t-hero">
        <div class="t-grid"></div>
        <div class="t-ring t-ring-1"></div>
        <div class="t-ring t-ring-2"></div>
        <div class="t-netline"></div>
        <div class="t-ball t-ball-1"></div>
        <div class="t-ball t-ball-2"></div>
        <div class="t-ball t-ball-3"></div>

        <div class="t-content">
          <span class="t-badge">Tennis Practice Notes</span>
          <h1 class="t-title">
            テニス
            <span class="t-accent">練習メモ</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="t-desc">
            コートで気づいたこと、体の感覚、改善のヒントを<br />
            ひとつひとつ丁寧に記録していく。
          </p>
          <a href="/blog" class="t-btn">記事一覧を見る &nbsp;→</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- STATS -->
      <div class="t-stats">
        <div class="t-stat"><div class="t-stat-n">壁</div><div class="t-stat-l">を意識する</div></div>
        <div class="t-stat"><div class="t-stat-n">体幹</div><div class="t-stat-l">で打つ</div></div>
        <div class="t-stat"><div class="t-stat-n">捻転</div><div class="t-stat-l">を効かせる</div></div>
        <div class="t-stat"><div class="t-stat-n">脱力</div><div class="t-stat-l">から爆発へ</div></div>
      </div>

      <!-- FEATURES -->
      <section class="t-features">
        <p class="t-sec-badge">About This Blog</p>
        <h2 class="t-sec-title">練習で気づいたことを<br />まとめています</h2>
        <div class="t-cards">
          <div class="t-card">
            <div class="t-card-ico">🎾</div>
            <h3 class="t-card-ttl">フォームの感覚</h3>
            <p class="t-card-txt">打つ瞬間の体の使い方、力の入れ方・抜き方のリアルな記録。理論より感覚を大切に。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="t-card">
            <div class="t-card-ico">💡</div>
            <h3 class="t-card-ttl">気づきのメモ</h3>
            <p class="t-card-txt">練習中にふと気づいた発見を忘れないうちに記録。小さな気づきが大きな改善につながる。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="t-card">
            <div class="t-card-ico">📈</div>
            <h3 class="t-card-ttl">改善の記録</h3>
            <p class="t-card-txt">壁を意識する、体幹で打つ、捻転を効かせる。課題と取り組みを継続的に追っていく。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="t-cta-wrap">
        <div class="t-cta">
          <div>
            <p class="t-cta-h">記事を読んで<br />一緒に上達しよう</p>
            <p class="t-cta-p">コートで使えるヒントが見つかるかも。</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/blog" class="t-cta-btn">記事一覧へ &nbsp;→</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
